Package org.neo4j.io.pagecache.impl.muninn

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AllocateFileTask  
    BackgroundTask
    A base class for page cache background tasks.
    CursorFactory  
    EvictionTask
    This Runnable runs the eviction algorithm.
    FileMapping  
    FreePage
    A free page in the MuninnPageCache.freelist.
    LatchMap
    The LatchMap is used by the MuninnPagedFile to coordinate concurrent page faults, and ensure that no two threads try to fault in the same page at the same time.
    LatchMap.Latch  
    MuninnPageCache
    The Muninn page cache implementation.
    MuninnPageCursor  
    MuninnPagedFile  
    MuninnReadPageCursor  
    MuninnWritePageCursor  
    OffHeapPageLock
    OffHeapPageLock is a sequence-based lock like StampedLock, but entirely non-blocking, and with special lock modes that are needed by the Muninn page cache.
    PageList
    The PageList maintains the off-heap meta-data for the individual memory pages.
    PreFetcher
    An adaptive page pre-fetcher for sequential scans, for either forwards (increasing page id order) or backwards (decreasing page id order) scans.
    StandalonePageCacheFactory  
    SwapperSet
    The SwapperSet maintains the set of allocated PageSwappers, and their mapping to swapper ids.
    SwapperSet.SwapperMapping
    The mapping entry between a PageSwapper and its swapper id.
    VictimPageReference  
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    CacheLiveLockException
    Thrown if a live-lock is encountered in the page cache.
    CursorExceptionWithPreciseStackTrace
    This exception is used to indicate in the stack trace, whether or not MuninnPageCursor.usePreciseCursorErrorStackTraces is enabled.
